# Selfies and video - Face Dataset

4,200+ sets in this dataset. Each person took a selfie on a webcam, took a selfie on a mobile phone. In addition, people recorded video from the phone and from the webcam, on which they pronounced a given set of numbers.

# 💴 For Commercial Usage: Full version of the dataset includes 34,000+ files, leave a request on **[TrainingData](https://trainingdata.pro/datasets/selfie-and-video?utm_source=kaggle&utm_medium=cpc&utm_campaign=selfies-and-video-dataset-4-000-people)** to buy the dataset

### Metadata for the full dataset:
- **assignment_id** - unique identifier of the media file
- **worker_id** - unique identifier of the person
- **age** - age of the person
- **true_gender** - gender of the person
- **country** - country of the person
- **ethnicity** - ethnicity of the person
- **media_1_extension, media_2_extension, media_5_extension, media_6_extension** - photo extensions in the dataset
- **media_1_resolution, media_2_resolution, media_5_resolution, media_6_resolution** - photo resolution in the dataset
- **media_3_extension, media_4_extension, media_7_extension, media_8_extension** - video extensions in the dataset
- **media_3_resolution, media_4_resolution, media_7_resolution, media_8_resolution** - video resolution in the dataset
- **media_3_fps, media_4_fps, media_7_fps, media_8_fps** - frames per second for video in the dataset
- **media_3_duration, media_7_duration** - duration of the long videos in the dataset
- **media_4_duration, media_8_duration** - duration of the short videos in the dataset

# Content

Includes folders corresponding to people in the dataset. Each folder includes 8 files (4 images and 4 videos).
